EASTERN NORTH ATLANTIC.
SCOTLAND.
DNC 19.
1. HAZARDOUS OPERATIONS 0900Z TO 2000Z DAILY

   57-24.9N 010-05.0W. VESSELS INTENDING TO ENTER

   VHF CH 16 OR PHONE: 187 060 4449 FOR ADVICE.
